tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_networking_equipment (
    equipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    equipment_name VARCHAR(255),
    manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
    configuration_settings JSON
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_networking_equipment (
  equipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  equipment_name VARCHAR(255),
  manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
  quantum_protocol VARCHAR(50),
  quantum_channel_state VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE network_configuration (
  configuration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  equipment_id INT,
  configuration_name VARCHAR(255),
  configuration_value VARCHAR(255),
  FOREIGN KEY (equipment_id) REFERENCES quantum_networking_equipment(equipment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_network_topology (
  topology_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  equipment_id INT,
  network_address VARCHAR(50),
  quantum_capacity INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (equipment_id) REFERENCES quantum_networking_equipment(equipment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE network_users (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  user_role VARCHAR(50),
  equipment_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (equipment_id) REFERENCES quantum_networking_equipment(equipment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_error_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  equipment_id INT,
  log_message TEXT,
  log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (equipment_id) REFERENCES quantum_networking_equipment(equipment_id)
);
